OL,6,FKhan, of Blagden Street in Sheffield,
OL,7,Fadmitted multiple counts of rape and
OL,8,Fwas jailed for 13 years at Bradford
OL,9,FCrown Court. He will serve an extended
OL,10,Fthree-year licence period.
OL,12,FActing Det Ch Insp Laura Casey, of
OL,13,FBradford District Safeguarding Team,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Khan was in a position of trust
OL,15,Fwhen he committed this horrific abuse
OL,16,Fon a child.
OL,18,F"As an imam, he was looked up to by
OL,19,Fstudents and family members within the
OL,20,Fcommunity.
